title: #144: Permanently Suspended with Anthony Cumia
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from Compound Media, Anthony Cumia, to discuss his new book "Permanently Suspended" and the history of censorship!
Thank you so much for all of your support.
Please check out my new special "Zero Fucks" on Vimeo.com
Vimeo.comn/ondemand/ZeroFucks
